{"tid":1902906,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[知乎] 2020年2月該如何評價大河內的動畫《罪惡王冠》？","createTime":"2020-02-28T15:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T15:48:55.000Z","uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"593cd6abc5e9eee21ae7364334cc8803079751a7","tid":1902906,"uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:26:20.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/374783708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F374783708&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJLV8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=d76d5bad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/374783708</a><br />\n那時候，我們怎樣評價《罪惡王冠》的故事？<br />\n<br />\n劇情喂屎、極度中二、放飛自我&hellip;&hellip;反正都是難聽的詞，有個別善良的觀眾，看我們罵得太狠，還會貼心地提醒一下大河內：&ldquo;大河內公子，該吃藥了。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WWYn88e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWYn88e.jpg&h=b63737d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過到了現在，情況卻完全不同。任何人在想黑大河內之前，都要好好地考慮一下&mdash;&mdash;說不定哪天，他的&ldquo;預言&rdquo;就成真了。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為，日本剛剛發生的事和《罪惡王冠》中的故事，實在是太像了。</span>"},{"pid":"81a3b408330d10dcc5ce102cabe541db3cbac982","tid":1902906,"uid":94312,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">同樣是病毒肆虐的世界；同樣是在疫情嚴重的情況下舉辦了一場大型集會；集會的理由也同樣離譜&mdash;&mdash;《罪惡王冠》是因為&ldquo;讓大家熱鬧一下&rdquo;，而現實中是要給新即位的天皇過一個生日。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5cwh5j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5cwh5j.jpg&h=aaa2cc77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誰也沒想到，這個在動畫裡被我們瘋狂吐槽的情節，真的在8年後的現實中發生了。而做出這件事的人，還都是日本的皇室和政府高層。<br />\n<br />\n《罪惡王冠》的故事，一下子有了魔幻現實主義的味道。"},{"pid":"2ee1bcdeeec3dd29abdaf0743e4a65696a656784","tid":1902906,"uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"其實，大河內&ldquo;未卜先知&rdquo;的事蹟，也不只這一件。<br />\n<br />\n早在年前，大河內的另一個代表作品《革命機Valvrave》就已經因為奇跡般地預測了&ldquo;學生建國&rdquo;而評分大漲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3PUCdD2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3PUCdD2.jpg&h=fc6b1235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當時，在香港混亂的局勢下，香港中文大學宣佈&ldquo;獨立&rdquo;，出入需要經過安檢，並且有計劃廢除港幣&hellip;&hellip;</span><br />\n而在《革命機Valvrave》中，<span style=\"color: red;\">同樣也有著同樣的橋段&mdash;&mdash;學生建國、校園憲法、混亂的男女關係、需要依靠興奮劑維持的暴力機構</span>&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n不過，就當整件事的熱度滿滿消退的時候，便有了最近的話題&mdash;&mdash;"},{"pid":"29199184f0929705281d7eb3fd16ff3a991d44b2","tid":1902906,"uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2ee1bcdeeec3dd29abdaf0743e4a65696a656784","tid":1902906,"uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"其實，大河內&ldquo;未卜先知&rdquo;的事蹟，也不只這一件。<br />\n<br />\n早在年前，大河內的另一個代表作品《革命機Valvrave》就已經因為奇跡般地預測了&ldquo;學生建國&rdquo;而評分大漲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3PUCdD2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3PUCdD2.jpg&h=fc6b1235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當時，在香港混亂的局勢下，香港中文大學宣佈&ldquo;獨立&rdquo;，出入需要經過安檢，並且有計劃廢除港幣&hellip;&hellip;</span><br />\n而在《革命機Valvrave》中，<span style=\"color: red;\">同樣也有著同樣的橋段&mdash;&mdash;學生建國、校園憲法、混亂的男女關係、需要依靠興奮劑維持的暴力機構</span>&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n不過，就當整件事的熱度滿滿消退的時候，便有了最近的話題&mdash;&mdash;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:29:37.000Z","msg":"廢除港幣未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb93d19684b92c8616ae1d3a9193386c16cd2f5","tid":1902906,"uid":94312,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:31:25.000Z","msg":"唔記得tag奇文共賞, 已經手動轉左繁體, sorry自拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b60b040db95f3083940947d7b02e83c5de2602","tid":1902906,"uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:32:45.000Z","msg":"然後再過倆月，日本宣佈處理不了病毒，並且建立甲鐵城[飆淚笑]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"